        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thanks! Can you get #b20 #t4000009#s, #t4000013#s, #t4000016#s, and #t4000019#s#k? Are you worried that it'll be too boring to hunt weak monsters? Hehe... well, this is just the beginning~ Then I'll leave it to you!"
